INSERT INTO `product_ranges` VALUES (1,'Amy','2009-05-27 11:46:27','2009-06-23 11:50:49','Location_Amy.jpg','image/jpeg',162615,'2009-06-23 11:50:48','The Amy is slightly more angular than many of our “Classic” chairs and has a neat, narrow footprint. The range includes models with different skirt lengths all of which can be supplied with a 1 or 2 inch cushion; there is also a full Drop-in cushion Model.'),(2,'Apollo','2009-05-27 11:47:26','2009-07-30 10:20:29','Location_Apollo.jpg','image/jpeg',163192,'2009-06-11 08:58:31','The Apollo is a modern high backed chair with rectangular tapered legs.  It is available with either padded weave seat or a fabric seat – all variations have the option of double weave backs.'),(3,'Babbington','2009-05-27 13:39:39','2009-08-17 07:50:54','Location_Babbington.jpg','image/jpeg',159765,'2009-06-11 08:59:16','This relatively new model is ideal for conservatories meant for lounging in.   The range includes a deep comfortable armchair and  two and three seater sofas.   There is also an accompanying footstool and sofa table.   The Babbingtons are available in all colours, including the Farrow and Ball ranges and with many standard fabrics – or indeed your own fabric if that is what you prefer.'),(4,'Balmoral','2009-05-27 13:40:08','2009-07-30 10:21:13','Location_Balmoral.jpg','image/jpeg',148752,'2009-06-11 09:02:02','The Balmoral is a classic design that lives up to its name.   It is a large, comfortable and curvaceous armchair with a padded weave seat.'),(5,'Bantam','2009-05-27 13:40:48','2009-07-30 10:21:29','Location_Bantam.jpg','image/jpeg',179690,'2009-06-11 09:02:44','The Bantam is one of our most popular dining chairs.   It is a relatively small, neat chair, ideal for the home environment or for restaurants.   It is available with either weave or fabric seats.   All models are also available with the option of double weave back and/or arms.     '),(6,'Burghley','2009-06-04 14:06:03','2009-08-21 11:18:43','Burghley_Location2.jpg','image/jpeg',174919,'2009-08-21 11:18:43','The original classic Lloydloom armchair, bringing back the elegance of the past but still perfect for today’s conservatories.    The model is available in many guises.   Both armchair and sofa come with either a drop-in cushion seat, as in the location shot, or with a padded or flat weave seat.   The flat weave seat is often ordered with either 1” or 2” cushions making it ideal for casual dining in restaurants or the home.   There are several tables that go well with the Burghley – look at the Burghley, Canterbury, Belvoir or Babbington tables.    The Babbington footstool is also a good match.'),(7,'Barcelona','2009-06-04 14:08:29','2009-07-30 10:23:08','Barcelona_Location.jpg','image/jpeg',134369,'2009-06-11 09:04:09','One of our most luxiourious models.   These chairs are extremely large and very comfortable.'),(8,'Bolero','2009-06-04 14:09:12','2009-07-30 10:23:35','Location_Bolero.jpg','image/jpeg',135257,'2009-06-11 09:04:59','One of our most admired models from the last 10 years, combing the traditional lloydloom features with a more contemporary line.   It is striking either as a single chair for the bedroom or reception – or as a casual dining chair - as it has been used in many restaurants and cafes.   It is available with either a weave or fabric seat.'),(9,'Bossanova','2009-06-04 14:10:12','2009-07-30 10:24:51','Location_Bossanova.jpg','image/jpeg',182588,'2009-06-09 14:24:13','The Bossanova is most often used for casual dining – but is at home wherever a comfortable and supportive seat is required.   It is exceptionally strong and available with a weave or fabric seat or a 3” drop in cushion.'),(10,'Boston','2009-06-04 14:10:57','2009-07-30 10:26:04','Location_Boston.jpg','image/jpeg',138572,'2009-06-11 09:05:42','An elegant and substantial dining chair that is very popular as a carver. Available with either a padded or a flat weave seats.   The flat weave seat is often ordered with a 1” or 2” cushion.   All versions of the chair can be provided fully upholstered.'),(11,'Boston Lounge','2009-06-04 14:11:45','2009-07-30 10:26:31','Boston_Lounge_Location.jpg','image/jpeg',167984,'2009-06-11 09:06:33','A lounge set with a more contemporary appeal to look at home in any interior setting.   It is designed for comfort with carefully upholstered cushions and a higher back for support.   The range includes a comfortable chair,   2 and 3 seater sofas and a substantial footstool.'),(13,'Childrens','2009-06-04 14:13:35','2009-08-21 12:56:17','Location_Childrens.jpg','image/jpeg',341616,'2009-08-21 12:56:16','Our popular children’s range is very strong and ideal for turning upside down and climbing on!   There are 4 chair shapes to chose from and one little table.'),(14,'Cumberland','2009-06-04 14:14:26','2009-07-30 10:27:35','Location_Cumberland.jpg','image/jpeg',116686,'2009-06-11 09:08:40','A classic from the last century with a 4” drop in cushion that can be upholstered in your own fabric if you wish.'),(15,'Delos Cubes','2009-06-04 14:15:04','2009-07-30 10:27:58','Location_Delos_Cubes.jpg','image/jpeg',117725,'2009-06-11 09:10:15','A very versatile contemporary range which can be used as occasional furniture in a modern setting or to complement our luxury leather furniture such as the “Quadra” chair.    The range includes various seats and tables and lends itself to bespoke work should you want something different.'),(16,'Derby','2009-06-04 14:15:59','2009-08-06 10:26:24','Derby_Location.jpg','image/jpeg',153699,'2009-06-11 09:11:11','This modern dining chair has square section tapered legs with a low weave back.   It is particularly popular in the model with arms, as shown above, and this version is available with a high or low back.  There is a “Naturals” weave version called the “Sereno”.'),(17,'Oxford','2009-06-04 14:16:42','2010-07-06 08:35:32','Location_Fireside.jpg','image/jpeg',114224,'2010-07-06 08:35:32','This armchair was designed to give comfort at an affordable price. There is a matching 2-seater sofa in the range.   Cushions for both are available in all our standard fabrics or can be made in the fabric of your choice.'),(18,'Lincoln','2009-06-04 14:17:36','2009-08-06 10:27:12','Location_Lincoln.jpg','image/jpeg',132799,'2009-06-11 09:12:57','A simple and classic Lloyd loom dining chair with a medium skirt and padded seat.'),(19,'Madrid','2009-06-04 14:18:21','2009-08-06 10:32:58','Madrid_Location.jpg','image/jpeg',152497,'2009-06-11 09:15:14','A plain sofa and matching chair which does not follow the more usual bent-wood designs of the classic Lloydloom chair.   It works well in reception areas.   See also the Valencia which is very similar with larger shaped arms.'),(20,'Nemo','2009-06-04 14:20:25','2009-08-06 10:28:05','Location_Mono.jpg','image/jpeg',162846,'2009-08-04 13:41:21','One of our modern Classics and nominated as such by many critics.   It is a remarkably well priced statement piece that needs to be seen to be fully appreciated.\r\n\r\n'),(21,'Neusis','2009-06-04 14:23:26','2009-08-06 10:30:48','location_Neusis.jpg','image/jpeg',159822,'2009-06-11 09:25:25','A classic bar stool that come in three heights to suit table, work top or bar.   It is also available with a weave back as the “Athene”.'),(22,'Newmarket','2009-06-04 14:35:03','2009-08-06 10:30:25','Newmarket_Location.jpg','image/jpeg',438852,'2009-07-08 10:49:28','A classic dining chair from the 1930’s.   Still appropriate in many  settings.   The Newmarket also comes in a bar stool height version.'),(23,'Orient','2009-06-04 14:37:50','2009-08-06 10:31:11','Orient_Location.jpg','image/jpeg',159790,'2009-06-11 09:27:36','Another classic from the 1930’s named after ss-Orient, the cruise ship.  It has a 4” drop-in cushion which can be upholstered in any of our standard fabrics or in the fabric of your choice.   The seat height is slightly lower than many of our casual dining chairs although it has been successfully used for dining in some locations.'),(24,'Orion','2009-06-04 14:39:49','2009-08-06 10:31:28','Location_Orion.jpg','image/jpeg',122214,'2009-06-11 09:28:13','This Lloyd Loom bed is a simple modern design.    There are alternative headboard heights available.   It is made in European rather than UK standard sizes so if you are from the UK, please speak to us before ordering.'),(25,'Belvoir','2009-06-08 12:31:28','2009-08-20 14:48:46','Location_Belvoir.jpg','image/jpeg',460433,'2009-08-20 14:48:45','One of our most popular chairs which takes up less room than the similar but more curvaceous Burghley.   It is available with an integral 4” drop-in cushion, very comfortable – or as a casual dining chair with either a padded or flat weave seat.   The flat weave seat is often used with a 1” or 2” cushion which is available in any of our standard fabrics or in the fabric of your choice.'),(26,'Winsover','2009-06-08 12:48:08','2009-08-06 10:32:09','Location_Winsover.jpg','image/jpeg',128766,'2009-06-11 09:29:39','A substantial and elegant armchair most often used as an occasional chair.   It is available with a 4” drop in cushion or a flat weave seat with a separate 1 or 2 inch cushion if required.    '),(27,'York','2009-06-08 12:58:52','2009-08-06 10:33:34','York_Location_Lo_Res.jpg','image/jpeg',362939,'2009-07-08 10:50:40','A popular and reasonably priced dining chair with a padded weave seat and either a medium or mini straight skirt or a sloping skirt as shown above.'),(28,'Bistro','2009-06-08 13:50:13','2009-08-06 10:35:55','Location_Bistro.jpg','image/jpeg',153010,'2009-06-11 09:31:07','One of our most popular small dining chairs ideal for the kitchen or for café/restaurants.   It is available in several forms all with a padded seat in either weave or any of our fabrics, including those recommended for contract situations.'),(29,'Stamford','2009-06-09 12:00:36','2009-08-06 10:36:21','Stamford_Location.jpg','image/jpeg',162572,'2009-06-11 09:31:35','One of the original Lloyd Loom of Spalding classics, available with different skirt depths and with a padded weave or fabric seat.   It is also available with a flat weave seat which version suits a 1” or 2” loose cushion.   All versions are also available with arms.   There is a matching Stamford table in several standard sizes.'),(30,'Wells','2009-06-09 12:44:46','2009-08-06 10:36:37','Location_Wells.jpg','image/jpeg',128960,'2009-06-11 09:32:20','A very elegant high backed dining chair with a padded seat in either weave or any of our standard fabrics.  Or with the fabric of your choice.'),(34,'Quadra','2009-06-11 09:34:00','2009-08-06 10:36:53','Location_Quadra.jpg','image/jpeg',115127,'2009-06-11 09:33:59','One of our most luxurious chairs which is available only with high quality leather upholstery – in a variety of colours.   It is shown here with a “Cube” table – and is often paired with other items from the Cube range.'),(35,'Riverside','2009-06-11 09:34:31','2009-08-06 10:37:45','Riverside_Location.jpg','image/jpeg',174680,'2009-06-11 09:34:30','A luxurious upholstered leather sofa and armchair with matching weave panels.   It is available only in our luxury leather range.'),(36,'Valencia','2009-06-11 09:35:05','2009-08-06 10:38:04','Valencia_Location.jpg','image/jpeg',152248,'2009-06-11 09:35:05','A large sofa and chair similar to the Madrid set. Often used in reception areas.'),(37,'Trader','2009-06-11 09:36:19','2009-09-03 08:21:21','Location_Bedroom.jpg','image/jpeg',140682,'2009-06-11 09:36:19','From our historic “Trader” range.   A matching bedside table, dressing table and low stool – available in any colour.'),(38,'Wave','2009-06-11 09:37:25','2009-08-06 10:40:49','Location_Wave.jpg','image/jpeg',123479,'2009-06-11 09:37:25','A comfortable high backed dining chair with a sinuous shaped back.   It is available with either a fabric or padded weave seat.'),(39,'Oyster','2009-06-12 14:00:13','2009-08-06 10:41:01','Location_Oyster.jpg','image/jpeg',69171,'2009-06-12 14:00:13','The Oyster range was designed by Nigel Coates and uses “Loomtex” instead of our more standard wired weave.   Loomtex is woven from spun paper and linen and is available in a limited range of colours.'),(33,'Zeus','2009-06-11 08:57:48','2009-08-06 10:41:13','Location_Zeus.jpg','image/jpeg',179348,'2009-06-11 08:57:47','A neat modern dining chair with square section tapered legs.   This model  is also available in the “Naturals” range as the “Maia”.    Both chairs are available with either padded weave or fabric seats.'),(62,'Outdoor Tables','2009-07-29 13:23:03','2009-08-20 14:54:47','Location_Tables.jpg','image/jpeg',133754,'2009-08-20 14:54:46','The Cordoba table range is available in square, round or oval versions.   They are all suitable for outdoor use and woven from the same rehau cord as our all-weather chair collection.  The furniture is fully UV resistant and weatherproof.   The tables are available in Mocha, Dark brown and  Antique Natural.    There is also a round table and a copy of our “Canterbury” indoor table in Whitewash colour.'),(41,'Naturals Maia','2009-06-18 08:26:02','2009-08-06 10:41:29','Location_Maia.jpg','image/jpeg',358652,'2009-07-02 08:55:15','This dining chair which is the same shape as the Zeus uses our new “Naturals” weave and features polished oak, walnut or beech legs in their natural state.   Made using traditional Lloyd Loom machinery, “Naturals” weave is made from 40% recycled paper which has been pre-dyed throughout, meaning that it does not have to be colour sprayed.   It is colour-fast and extremely hard wearing with no possibility of the colour chipping or rubbing – and it is therefore ideal for any challenging or contract situation.'),(56,'Tables Apollo','2009-07-02 12:49:10','2009-07-02 12:49:10',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,''),(57,'Tables Bistro','2009-07-02 12:49:21','2009-08-20 14:56:53','Location_Bistro_Tables.jpg','image/jpeg',113858,'2009-08-20 14:56:53',''),(58,'Tables Burghley','2009-07-02 12:49:34','2009-08-20 14:58:07','Location_Belvoir_Tables.jpg','image/jpeg',98734,'2009-08-20 14:58:07',''),(44,'Naturals Sereno','2009-06-18 08:27:23','2009-08-06 10:50:45','Location_Sereno.jpg','image/jpeg',159445,'2009-06-18 08:27:23','This dining chair which is the same shape as the Derby uses our new “Naturals” weave and features polished oak, walnut or beech legs in their natural state.  Made using traditional Lloyd Loom machinery, “Naturals” weave is made from 40% recycled paper which has been pre-dyed throughout, meaning that it does not have to be colour sprayed.   It is colour-fast and extremely hard wearing with no possibility of the colour chipping or rubbing – and it is therefore ideal for any challenging or contract situation.   The Sereno comes with or without arms.'),(45,'Naturals Laziz','2009-06-18 08:34:52','2009-08-06 10:51:03','Location_Laziz.jpg','image/jpeg',116163,'2009-06-18 08:34:52','This is the “Naturals” version of the “Athene” stool and features polished oak, walnut or beech legs in their natural state.   “Naturals” weave, made using traditional Lloyd Loom machinery, uses 40% recycled paper which has been pre-dyed throughout, meaning that it does not have to be colour sprayed.   It is colour-fast and extremely hard wearing with no possibility of the colour chipping or rubbing – and it is therefore ideal to any challenging or contract situation.'),(55,'Tables Stamford','2009-06-30 08:10:33','2009-08-20 15:12:27','Location.jpg','image/jpeg',227269,'2009-08-20 15:12:26',''),(47,'Outdoor Belvoir','2009-06-18 08:58:06','2009-08-06 10:51:34','Location_Belvoir.jpg','image/jpeg',373935,'2009-07-02 13:44:04','This outdoor model is a copy of our traditional Lloydloom indoor Belvoir.  Our normal paper weave is unsuitable for outdoor use and instead we recommend the all-weather collection which is woven from rehau cord.   The furniture is fully UV resistant and weatherproof.  There are also 1” and 2” loose cushions available.   The Belvoir is available in colours Whitewash or Antique Natural .  There are matching tables in both these colours.'),(48,'Outdoor Bolero','2009-06-18 09:01:26','2009-08-06 10:51:47','Location_Bolero.jpg','image/jpeg',284855,'2009-07-02 13:47:51','This outdoor model is a copy of our traditional Lloydloom indoor Bolero.  Our normal paper weave is unsuitable for outdoor use and instead we recommend the all-weather collection which is woven from rehau cord.   The furniture is fully UV resistant and weatherproof.   The Belvoir is available in colours Mocha or Antique Natural.  There are also 1” and 2” loose cushions available.'),(49,'Outdoor Bossanova','2009-06-18 09:03:35','2009-08-06 10:52:10','Location_Bossanova.jpg','image/jpeg',263758,'2009-07-02 13:48:22','This outdoor model is a copy of our traditional Lloydloom indoor Bossanova.  Our normal paper weave is unsuitable for outdoor use and instead we recommend the all-weather collection which is woven from rehau cord.   The furniture is fully UV resistant and weatherproof.   The Bossanova is available in colours Mocha or Antique Natural.   There are also 1” and 2” loose cushions available.'),(50,'Outdoor Boston','2009-06-18 09:05:13','2009-08-06 10:52:23','Location_Boston.jpg','image/jpeg',266495,'2009-07-02 13:42:19','This outdoor model is a copy of our traditional Lloydloom indoor Boston dining chair.  Our normal paper weave is unsuitable for outdoor use and instead we recommend the all-weather collection which is woven from rehau cord.   The furniture is fully UV resistant and weatherproof.   The Boston is available with or without arms and in the colour “Dark Brown”.'),(51,'Outdoor Cordoba','2009-06-18 09:06:42','2009-08-06 10:52:38','Location_Cordoba.jpg','image/jpeg',239020,'2009-07-02 13:32:39','The Cordoba sofa and chair are comfortable outdoor pieces with cushions available in any of our standard fabrics or in showerproof “Sunbrella”.  Our normal paper weave is unsuitable for outdoor use and instead we recommend the all-weather collection which is woven from rehau cord.   The furniture is fully UV resistant and weatherproof.   The Cordoba set is available in colours Mocha and Antique Natural.   There is also a footstool, coffee table and lounger available in the range.'),(52,'Outdoor Cubes','2009-06-18 09:07:42','2009-08-06 10:52:54','Location_Cubes.jpg','image/jpeg',288502,'2009-07-02 13:32:01','The cubes which can be used as seats, fit under the cube table which can be ordered separately.   There is also a matching coffee table within the range.   The set is woven from rehau cord and is fully UV resistant and weatherproof.   The range is available in colours Mocha or Antique Natural.'),(61,'Linen Baskets','2009-07-28 10:20:49','2009-07-28 10:20:49','kp1linen.jpg','image/jpeg',121559,'2009-07-28 10:20:48',''),(59,'Tables Belvoir','2009-07-02 12:49:42','2009-08-20 15:08:39','Location_Belvoir_Table.jpg','image/jpeg',169154,'2009-08-20 15:08:39',''),(60,'Tables Canterbury','2009-07-02 12:49:51','2009-08-21 11:04:37','Canterbury_location.jpg','image/jpeg',360490,'2009-08-21 11:04:37',''),(64,'Outdoor Bantam','2009-08-07 10:43:33','2009-08-07 10:43:33','Location_Bantams.jpg','image/jpeg',428817,'2009-08-07 10:43:32','This neat all-weather dining chair is available with or without arms.   Our normal paper weave is unsuitable for outdoor use and instead we recommend the all-weather collection which is woven from rehau cord.   The furniture is fully UV resistant and weatherproof.   The Bantam is available in Mocha or Antique Natural.   There are also 1” and 2” loose cushions available.'),(70,'Beeby','2010-02-25 15:12:44','2010-02-25 15:12:44','Location_Beeby.jpg','image/jpeg',135044,'2010-02-25 15:12:44',''),(69,'Athene','2009-08-21 11:20:22','2009-08-21 11:22:40','Athene_Location.jpg','image/jpeg',113876,'2009-08-21 11:22:39','');
